  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/d380b3edc4c3ff8d7a067a1d3eb27753.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/d380b3edc4c3ff8d7a067a1d3eb27753.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/d380b3edc4c3ff8d7a067a1d3eb27753.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The humans destroyed the world but one brave ape becomes the last hope to save the world of animals from evil. During the journey, you will face dangerous armies, creatures, robots and much... much more! The fate of this world is in your hands. Discover, upgrade, fight and become the legend in your tale. Traverse the world from ancient times to the future. Gather tokens then upgrade your character in many ways. The Ape Tales combine the good old platform games with the new standards of modern games! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/a7ce455ac3ae9e417ccd20f5a06e2fa3.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/a7ce455ac3ae9e417ccd20f5a06e2fa3.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/a7ce455ac3ae9e417ccd20f5a06e2fa3.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Every level gives you other experiences, challenges and stories!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 10+ maps with new challenges on your way to your success!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From sandy islands, forests, and caves to the darkest corners of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone will find something for themselves in many worlds of The Ape Tales.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/ec118e350d2639da79057938defa8aa9.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/ec118e350d2639da79057938defa8aa9.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/ec118e350d2639da79057938defa8aa9.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face unique enemies on every map!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with over 35+ enemies and become a legend who saves the world from evil!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knights, aliens, dinosaurs, robots and pirates are only a small example of this journey.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e0da6ef528fa1edd1521dfe011ef4b48.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e0da6ef528fa1edd1521dfe011ef4b48.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e0da6ef528fa1edd1521dfe011ef4b48.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the greatest adventure of your life in your style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Upgrade your weapon, change your look and choose your ability. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot the bananas, shurikens and change your appearance to a knight ape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire new abilities to become more powerful than you can imagine!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/4f0907494ea8b5cb7ecc36ad5d5e6721.avif?t=1759614579\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ape Tales: An Epic Adventure Game</strong> features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 12+ maps, each with different enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the dwellers and make quests to unlock the epilogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every map means a new challenging boss to encounter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect tokens and buy new weapons, abilities and skins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel from prehistoric to the future world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and much... much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our epic adventure now, and help the world to be better! The lands hide many secrets that are waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e6763dc6386a1344c8c6515147d171a0.avif?t=1759614579\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/d380b3edc4c3ff8d7a067a1d3eb27753.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/d380b3edc4c3ff8d7a067a1d3eb27753.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/d380b3edc4c3ff8d7a067a1d3eb27753.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The humans destroyed the world but one brave ape becomes the last hope to save the world of animals from evil. During the journey, you will face dangerous armies, creatures, robots and much... much more! The fate of this world is in your hands. Discover, upgrade, fight and become the legend in your tale. Traverse the world from ancient times to the future. Gather tokens then upgrade your character in many ways. The Ape Tales combine the good old platform games with the new standards of modern games! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/a7ce455ac3ae9e417ccd20f5a06e2fa3.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/a7ce455ac3ae9e417ccd20f5a06e2fa3.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/a7ce455ac3ae9e417ccd20f5a06e2fa3.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Every level gives you other experiences, challenges and stories!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 10+ maps with new challenges on your way to your success!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From sandy islands, forests, and caves to the darkest corners of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone will find something for themselves in many worlds of The Ape Tales.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/ec118e350d2639da79057938defa8aa9.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/ec118e350d2639da79057938defa8aa9.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/ec118e350d2639da79057938defa8aa9.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face unique enemies on every map!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with over 35+ enemies and become a legend who saves the world from evil!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knights, aliens, dinosaurs, robots and pirates are only a small example of this journey.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e0da6ef528fa1edd1521dfe011ef4b48.poster.avif?t=1759614579\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e0da6ef528fa1edd1521dfe011ef4b48.webm?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e0da6ef528fa1edd1521dfe011ef4b48.mp4?t=1759614579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the greatest adventure of your life in your style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Upgrade your weapon, change your look and choose your ability. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot the bananas, shurikens and change your appearance to a knight ape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire new abilities to become more powerful than you can imagine!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/4f0907494ea8b5cb7ecc36ad5d5e6721.avif?t=1759614579\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Ape Tales: An Epic Adventure Game</strong> features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 12+ maps, each with different enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the dwellers and make quests to unlock the epilogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every map means a new challenging boss to encounter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect tokens and buy new weapons, abilities and skins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel from prehistoric to the future world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and much... much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our epic adventure now, and help the world to be better! The lands hide many secrets that are waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2608600/extras/e6763dc6386a1344c8c6515147d171a0.avif?t=1759614579\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p>",
